@startuml SD-05
skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam roundcorner 10
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.5
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBorderColor #888888
skinparam sequenceParticipantBorderColor #444444
skinparam sequenceParticipantFontSize 12
skinparam sequenceMessageFontSize 11

title SD-05: Feedback User - Jawaban Benar

actor "Pengunjung\n(Browser)" as User #4A90D9
participant "Laravel\n(ChatbotController)" as Laravel #2E8B57
participant "ChatbotService\n(Laravel)" as Service #50C878
database "MySQL\n(Database)" as DB #3498DB
participant "Flask\n(app.py)" as Flask #E67E22

== 1. User Klik Tombol "Benar" ==
User -> Laravel : POST /feedback\n{user_message: "dimana poli umum?",\nis_correct: true,\npredicted_room_id: 5, intent: "cari_ruangan"}
activate Laravel

== 2. Validasi Data Feedback ==
Laravel -> Service : saveFeedback(data)
activate Service
note right of Service
  Validasi input:
  - user_message: wajib diisi
  - is_correct: wajib boolean
  - predicted_room_id: opsional
end note

== 3. Simpan Feedback ke Database ==
Service -> DB : ChatbotFeedback::create({\nuser_message, is_correct: 1,\npredicted_room_id: 5, intent})
activate DB
DB --> Service : feedback tersimpan (id=42)
deactivate DB

== 4. Cek Apakah Perlu Sinkronisasi ==
note over Service
  is_correct = true
  is_intent_correct = null (dianggap benar)
  needSync = false
  Tidak perlu retraining model
end note

Service --> Laravel : {status: "success"}
deactivate Service

== 5. Kirim Konfirmasi ke User ==
Laravel --> User : JSON {status: "success"}
deactivate Laravel

note over User
  Browser tampilkan:
  "Terima kasih atas feedback Anda!"
  Tombol feedback hilang
end note

@enduml
